<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.2.4">
<l>cūḻcci ñāṉac cuṭaroḷi yākiyeṉṟu</l>
<l>mēḻccikē ṭiṉṟi yeṅkaṇu niṟaintaventāy</l>
<l>tāḻccimaṟ ṟēṅkun tavirntuniṉ ṟāḷiṇaikkīḻ</l>
<l>vāḻcciyāṉ cērum vakaiyaruḷāy vantē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O our father who pervades everywhere without loss in rising,</l>
<l>always being the glowing light of counsel [and] knowledge,</l>
<l>come [and] grace [me] with a manner of joining life</l>
<l>under the pair of your feet, refraining from any other subservience.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
